== 爭議 ==
2020年10月，世界[[印度教|印度教]]協會主席拉詹·澤德（{{lang-hi|Rajan Zed}}）向 Coamix 發表聲明，批評漫畫中對印度教神靈的描繪，要求該公司不要在作品裡輕視包含[[濕婆|濕婆]]在內的所有受尊崇印度教神靈和女神<ref>{{Cite web|last=Hazra|first=Adriana|date=October 15, 2020|title=Hindu U.S. Statesman Objects to Depiction of Deities in Manga|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/daily-briefs/2020-10-15/hindu-u.s-statesman-objects-to-depiction-of-deities-in-manga/.165118|access-date=December 23, 2020|website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]}}</ref> 。許多印裔美國人強烈反彈作中對濕婆的描繪，批評該動畫系列「輕視了他們的神明，令他們感到不安」<ref>{{Cite web|last=Patel|first=Madhu|title=Netflix urged not to run anime 'Record of Ragnarok'trivializing Lord Shiva|url=https://www.indiapost.com/netflix-urged-not-to-run-anime-record-of-ragnaroktrivializing-lord-shiva/|url-status=live|archive-url=https://archive.today/20210624173813/https://www.indiapost.com/netflix-urged-not-to-run-anime-record-of-ragnaroktrivializing-lord-shiva/|archive-date=June 24, 2021|access-date=June 24, 2021|website=India Post|date=15 April 2021 }}</ref>。Netflix為了避免進一步批評而修改了預告片以刪除動畫中濕婆的角色，後來更將動畫從印度分部的流媒體庫中刪除<ref>{{Cite web|last=Naik|first=Kshiteej|date=June 22, 2021|title=Netflix Hasn't Released Record of Ragnarok in India|url=https://in.ign.com/tv/161166/news/netflix-record-of-ragnarok-india-release-streaming|access-date=June 24, 2021|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|location=India}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Hazra|first=Adriana|date=June 27, 2021|title=Netflix Removes Record of Ragnarok Anime in India|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2021-06-27/netflix-removes-record-of-ragnarok-anime-in-india/.174482|access-date=June 27, 2021|website=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]}}</ref>

